99
00:07:11,094 --> 00:07:14,694
and put the blame on dad who was your superior, too!

100
00:07:14,694 --> 00:07:16,415
I know that!

101
00:07:16,415 --> 00:07:19,794
What... What're you talking about, Mai?

102
00:07:19,794 --> 00:07:22,421
I see, so she's the one.

103
00:07:22,421 --> 00:07:25,894
She's the one who...

104
00:07:25,894 --> 00:07:28,427
So, are you satisfied?

105
