Let my son go!

106
00:07:30,694 --> 00:07:33,494
Son? What's that about?

107
00:07:33,494 --> 00:07:37,594
You're made me do something like this with this letter, right?

108
00:07:37,594 --> 00:07:38,894
Letter?

109
00:07:38,894 --> 00:07:40,439
Please let me see it.

110
00:07:42,441 --> 00:07:44,094
I have your son.

111
00:07:44,094 --> 00:07:45,594
If you want him back,

112
00:07:45,594 --> 00:07:47,994
