223
00:13:33,794 --> 00:13:35,894
Let... Let me see it.

224
00:13:38,594 --> 00:13:41,794
And, what's come of the bomb scare?

225
00:13:41,794 --> 00:13:42,801
What?

226
00:13:43,894 --> 00:13:46,094
Mail from somebody he doesn't know?

227
00:13:49,694 --> 00:13:51,694
Who on earth can it be?

228
00:13:58,817 --> 00:14:02,070
Who on earth could've sent him this mail?

229
00:14:02,070 --> 00:14:03,870
The only thing I can say

230
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:05,570
