231
00:14:05,570 --> 00:14:09,770
on this floor till just a while ago.

232
00:14:09,770 --> 00:14:11,670
What's the matter, Conan?

233
00:14:11,670 --> 00:14:13,670
Nothing...

234
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:15,770
I was thinking that the person who sent this mail

235
00:14:15,770 --> 00:14:18,070
